{"tid":607453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵宣佈今年6月加價3.14%","createTime":"2018-03-27T10:14:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T01:13:29.000Z","uid":55851,"like":4,"dislike":94,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"74d156bdf184c23cd383ea1191704cc36db03ad1","tid":607453,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T10:14:07.000Z","msg":"港鐵今年6月加價重臨！隨著政府今公布去年第4季運輸業名義工資變動數字，港鐵具體票價加幅亦揭盅。現時「可加可減機制」可計算今年票價調整幅度，參考最新公布的數據推算，若連同「追加」去年凍結的加幅即1.49%，預計港鐵今年加價3.14%。<br />\n<br />\n另外，港鐵今年會撥出2億元作票價優惠，連同去年錄得10宗31分鐘或以上的延誤事故，需罰款2,250萬元，換言之，今年港鐵合共有2.225億元，用作提供不少於半年的每程九七折回贈優惠。<br />\n<br />\n實政圓桌立法會議員田北辰說，港鐵今年業績錄得破紀錄盈餘的168億元，仍加價3.14%，令市民反感，「俾人個觀感好曳」，會爭取港鐵在現行加幅上每年再額外扣減1.5%，令今年加幅僅1.64%，方可「勉強收貨」。"},{"pid":"a942596cb22df22d700e7f4c6f72e956f6b32f22","tid":607453,"uid":33651,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T10:14:39.000Z","msg":"馬時亨我屌你老母"},{"pid":"5e55a8d292aedd1a41604d2dee8d7917fae086e4","tid":607453,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T10:14:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c994fc6efe5978ce3b30513c9c2df1292978b9","tid":607453,"uid":55851,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T10:15:31.000Z","msg":"連登仔無論如何都會堅持比正價，係港鐵忠實顧客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb934e0027a03ddeafd9325e9077a65090f23f4","tid":607453,"uid":16123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T10:15:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets